        <pre>
            Zoho | Cloud Operations Engineer Hiring
Job Title : Cloud Operations Engineer
Work Location: Chennai
Experience : 1 -5 Years

Job Description:
Candidates should have good knowledge in Linux OS and cloud infrastructure components like virtualization, Load Balancers, etc.
Candidates will be part of Cloud and Infra operations team who is responsible to manage Zoho's various Data Centers located across the globe.

Data Center management includes complete lifecycle of servers, storage servers and other supporting systems.

Should be interested to work in 24x7 rotational shift, which includes monitoring of servers & Zoho applications and prepare RCA for any incidents.

Configuration and provisioning of Linux OS for large number of servers using automated installation methods.

Management of various infrastructure components such as DNS/ DHCP/ NTP/ Proxy/ OS Image Servers / Load Balancers.

Work includes periodic validation of DR data centers across the globe.

Good knowledge in different open source tools like Puppet / Ansible for automation and other tasks like package management.

Knowledge in shell / python scripts.

Knowledge in basic networking concepts like VLAN, NAT, ARP, basic FW and Switch configuration.

Basic knowledge in SaaS components like RDBMS, NoSQL, Hadoop, etc.

Knowledge in server hardware components like CPU, different types of drives, internal design / connectivity, etc.

Good co-ordination & communications skills to work with different nature of teams ( ex. network, framework , devops, application development and support teams )

Must be able to work effectively with minimum supervision and handle multiple priorities.

Candidates should have interest in learning new technologies in OS, servers hardware, cloud components, etc
